More and more forces mobilized for giant strike
On Friday, the League of Trade Unions and the Hungarian Trade Union Federation will form their coordination committee for the indefinite duration of the strike beginning on Monday.
On Saturday a large-scale protest assembly will be held, on Monday - on the day of the referendum on the Health Insurance Act - the stoppage of work begins.
