"Szezon" by Ferenc Török).
The formation, which had initially appeared in smaller clubs, only became known to the wider audience when the magazine "wan2" ranked their first album from 2002 among the top 50 domestic albums and, together with Yonderboi, named Zagar the almost only trendsetter that was also marketable in the West.
