On Wednesday, no agreement was reached on the future status of the province at the last negotiating meeting in Vienna.
At the end of the failure
The Serbs and Albanians from Kosovo concluded a sixth and final discussion session in Baden, Austria, Wednesday morning, without being able to overcome their controversy over the future status of the separatist province.
